# Project Architecture Context

## Structure
```
backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/
├── adapters/       # External integrations (DB repos, cache, HTTP clients)
├── application/    # Use cases, services, DTOs
├── config/         # Settings, logging, constants
├── core/           # Pure domain (entities, enums, interfaces, value objects)
├── infrastructure/ # DB engines, HTTP clients, security, profiling
├── ports/          # API routes, CLI, webhooks, DI container
└── utils/          # Shared utilities
```

## Dependency Rule
`adapters → ports → application → core`
Application services access repos via UoW properties (`uow.users`), never by importing concrete adapters.

## Key Files
- `registry/naming_registry.json` — Single source of truth for shared identifiers
- `opencode.json` — OpenCode configuration (plugins, MCP, permissions)
- `.opencode/oh-my-opencode.jsonc` — oh-my-opencode plugin configuration
- `Taskfile.yml` — Task runner commands (`task dev`, `task test`, `task lint`)
